The following image types are supported for the image:

@li JPEG 
@li PNG
@li GIF
@li BMP
@li WBMP
@li TIFF

\n
The following image types are supported for the mask:

@li JPEG 
@li PNG
@li GIF
@li BMP
@li WBMP
@li TIFF

